search_term: Find the official pricing page URL for Callingly (callingly.com). Only provide the exact URL to the pricing page, not a summary of pricing information.
response_text: The official pricing page for Callingly can be found at this URL: [https://callingly.com/pricing/](https://callingly.com/pricing/)【3:0†source】.

citations.title: Callingly | Free Trial and Pricing Plans

extracted_content.content:
Unlimited Plans
---------------

Unlimited minutes. Unlimited calls. You need it, you got it.

#### Voice

Call your hot leads within seconds

$25
---

per user

PER MONTH

**Unlimited** USA Call Minutes  
**Cheap** International Rates  
**Unlimited** Leads  
**$3** Local or Toll-Free Numbers  
Minimum **2** Users

No credit card required.

![Image 1](https://callingly.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pricing_Voice-185x200.png)

#### Voice + SMS

Call and message to double your results

$35
---

per user

PER MONTH

**Unlimited** USA Call Minutes  
**Unlimited** USA Texts  
**Cheap** International Rates  
**Unlimited** Leads  
**$3** Local or Toll-Free Numbers  
Minimum **2** Users

No credit card required.

![Image 2](https://callingly.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pricing_VoiceSMS-185x200.png)

Metered Plans
-------------

Your whole team on one plan, and share the minutes.

#### Realty Team

1,000 minutes and 1,000 texts for your whole team

$250
----

PER MONTH

**Unlimited** Users  
1,000 USA/Canada Minutes  
1,000 USA/Canada Texts  
**Unlimited** Leads  
**$3** Local or Toll-Free Numbers

_Overage: $50 for 500 extra minutes, $50 for 500 extra sms_

![Image 3](https://callingly.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/RealtyTeamPlan_Pricing-260x300.png)

##### Annual Plan

Save 20% when you buy annually. Start with the same free trial.

$200/month

For Larger Teams
----------------

Agencies, resellers and large organizations.

#### Agency

For agencies & resellers

Same **$25 or $35** per User  
**No Additional Fees**  
**Client Management** Panel  
**Custom** Domain

![Image 4](https://callingly.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pricing_Agency-185x200.png)

#### Enterprise

For large organizations

**Custom** Integrations  
**Custom** Terms of Service  
**Priority** Phone Support  
Service Level Agreement  
Contact Us for Pricing  
Starting at $2,000/m

![Image 5](https://callingly.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pricing_Enterprise-3-394x200.png)

Faster calls mean more sales
----------------------------

No credit card required.

Try Callingly lead response management software FREE for 14 days. View pricing for voice, voice + sms, and agency plans.
